text: Jean-Luc Force (born 31 March 1959) is a French equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
